Ms. N. T. Minh, born in 1955 (Member # 010107050021). Currently she raises 10 pigs for meat and a herd of piglets.  She is a school teacher but still increases production. Her husband and 2 children work for others and make extra income. Average income for her family is 177 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 250 USD to invest in her pig raising business. Also borrowing with her are:

Ms. N. T. H., born in 1957 (member # 010107050025); she is asking for loan amount of 250 USD to invest in raising chickens;
Ms. Hoang T. X., born in 1960 (member# 010107050023). She has a general store serving the local community. Average income for her family is 12 USD per month. She is looking for loan amount of 250 USD to invest in her general store;
 Ms. Hoang T. D., born in 1957 (member # 010107050022). Her family works in farming. Every day she sells vegetables at the market for income. She is looking for loan amount of 250 USD to make purchases at the market;
Ms. N. T. A. T., born in 1980 (member # 010107050024). She works in farming and selling vegetables. She is looking for loan amount of 250 USD to make purchases at the market.




