Ms. D. T. Thuy, born in 1956 (Member # 010107050032). She lives with her husband and 2 children in Van Thuong, Xuan Canh, Dong Anh, Ha Noi. Her husband is a construction worker with daily income; for herself she increases income by selling vegetables. Average income for her family is 117 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 290 USD to invest in raising pigs and cows. The other members in her loan group are:

Ms. Bui T. D. (member # 010107050034); joined the fund to borrow 245 USD to invest in her animal raising business and to make purchases at the market;
Ms. Hoang T. C., born in 1958 (member # 010107050033). She has a restaurant in the local community. Average income for her family is 12 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 245 USD to invest in her restaurant;
Ms, Hoang T. N., born in 1980 (member # 010107050036). Her family works in farming. Every day she goes to the market selling chickens and raising pigs. She joined the fund to borrow 245 USD to make purchases at the market;
Ms. Hoang T. L., born in 1946 (member # 010107050027). She joined the fund to borrow 245 USD to raise hens;
Ms. Dao T. N., born in 1976 (member # 010107050030). She joined the fund to borrow 245 USD to raise egg-laying ducks;
Ms. Nguyen T. H., born in 1971 (member # 010107050035). She joined the fund to borrow 295 USD to raise pigs and chickens;
Ms. Nguyen T. N., born in 1973 (member# 010107050028). She joined the fund to borrow 290 USD to invest in a refreshment shop selling sweets, sodas, beer etc)

<br /><p><strong>Translated from Vietnamese by Thu Ostrander, Kiva Volunteer</strong></p>

Ms. H. T. Ha, born in 1964 (member # 010107050001). She and her husband have 2 small children who are still in school. Her husband works outside the home with a stable income. In addition to farming, she also goes to the market to sell ready-to-eat items (chicken/pork pate, pork hash..). Average income for her family is 175 USD per month. She is the leader in her loan group and the other members are:

Ms. Nguyen T. T., born in 1972 (member #  010107050005). She joined the fund to borrow 245 USD to invest in a clothing shop. Average income for her family is 14 USD per month;
Ms. Dao T. P., born in 1977 (member #  010107050004). She joined the fund to borrow 195 USD to invest in raising hens;
Ms. H. T. M., born in 1978 (member # 010107050006). She works outside the home with a monthly income. She joined the fund to borrow 195 USD to invest in raising pigs. 
Ms. H. T. D., born in 1972 (member # 010107050003). In addition to raising animals, she also grows ornamental plants. Average income for her family is 15 USD per day. She joined the fund to borrow 245 USD to invest in raising animals;
